    "Description": "ATTENTION ALL FTL COURIERS\nFOR IMMEDIATE ASSIGNMENT\n\n**CONTRACT DETAILS** \n\nPICKUP LOCATION \u2013 An FTL ship carrying a delivery for Alliance Aid has not completed it's contract. The last known location has it still over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. A courier needed to retrieve package and continue delivery.\n\nDROPOFF LOCATION \u2013 Package must be taken to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Target|Address)</EM4>. \n\nTHREAT LEVEL \u2013 It is unclear what happened to the ship, but we expect a malfunction. Still, caution is advised. <EM4>Low level engagements</EM4> expected.\n\nTRAVEL \u2013  All transportation needs should be arranged by courier. \n\nFTL Courier Services\u00a0is proud to be assisting in Alliance Aid efforts to help fight the Levski outbreak.",
